<HEADLINE>
STARTERS ON LINE HUNGRY  
 ASU DEFENSIVE COACH TOUTS TALENT, DEPTH 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By PAOLA BOIVIN  
 c.1998 The Arizona Republic  
