   GLASS-COLUMN _ The initial phase of the telecom technology
upgrade, known as local number portability (LNP), should be in
place in the nation's top 100 markets by the end of the year. In
due course, number portability should expand from current
capabilities _ to keep a number when you change local providers _
to span services in any of the 50 states. (Glass, Cox News Service)
MOVED 7/30.
