<HEADLINE>
THANKS TO NEW TOOLS LIKE `THE WAND,' DENTAL PATIENTS FEELING LESS
PAIN
</HEADLINE>
 
(Stands for HEALTH-POIROT-COLUMN) (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By CAROLYN POIROT 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
