<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-31 20:06 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3019 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CANADA-CHEAP-BOS &LR;      07-31 1228
