7-31 -- Vistas like this, of the Yellowstone River near Park City,
draw a lot of people to Big Sky Country. But they also attract
runaway loners as troubled as the Unabomber and Russell Weston Jr.,
the man charged with killing two Capitol police officers. (Larry
Mayer/New York Times Photo)
</P>
