<P>
   INVESTMENT-BANKERS (Undated) _ The incredible shrinking
investment banker: Even as M&AMP;A reaches epic proportions, the role
of investment bankers in dealmaking has diminished. By Laura
Holson. (Moved). Graphic and Photo. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   IRS-ABUSE (Fort Worth, Texas) _ When Tex Moncrief became a
poster boy for IRS abuse, it was evidence that the demonization of
the tax collector had reached a new level. By Carol Marie Cropper.
(Moved). Photo. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Invest
</P>
<P>
   INVEST-CO-CEOs (subslug) (Undated) _ The Bell Atlantic-GTE deal
is the latest in which two people will share the title of chief
executive. But do these sharings of duties actually work, or is
this just a marriage of convenience that will cause more problems
